<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #0056b3;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            text-align: left; /* Keep text left-aligned */
        }
        .email-body p, .email-body h1 {
            text-align: left; /* Keep text left-aligned */
        }
        a:not(.button-link) { /* Apply styles only to links without .button-link class */
            color: #027BFF;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .button-link { /* Center the button and keep the text color white */
            display: block; /* Change to block to allow margin auto to work */
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 10px auto; /* Center the button */
            background-color: #027BFF;
            color: #ffffff; /* Ensure text is white */
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
            <p>You have requested to reset your password. Please click the button below to set a new password:</p>
            <br>
            <a href="{{link}}" target="_blank" class="button-link" style="color: #ffffff;" >Reset Password</a>
            <br>
            <p>This password reset link will expire in 30 minutes. If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email. If you're having trouble with the button above, click on the link below to reset your password.</p>
            <p>{{link}}</p>
            <p>Regards,<br>Fatima's Therapy Service</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>